<title>CHINA: Hansom yearly net loss HK$12.02 mln.</title>
<headline>Hansom yearly net loss HK$12.02 mln.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-08-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   5.6 loss   vs 11.4 loss</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    nil	  vs nil</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	  5.34 loss  vs 6.17 loss</p>
<p>    Net			    12.02 loss vs 24.31 loss</p>
<p>    Turnover		     54.71	vs 87.87 (see note)</p>
<p>    Company name		 Hansom Holdings Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		  N/A</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	   N/A</p>
<p>NOTE - Hansom is a construction group.</p>
<p>The sales of goods were not included in the last year's turnover.</p>
<p>Net is after an exceptional loss of HK$2.94 million on provision for diminution in value of investment in an associated company, loss of HK$1.21 million on provision for a doubtful debt and loss of HK$1.19 million on disposal of subsidiaries.</p>
<p>Total dividend for year is nil vs nil.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong News Room (852) 2843 6368</p>
